    "body": "It appears that `git` is printing invalid utf-8 for the upstream branch name:\n```\n# branch.oid 95627686a0f69732baba5b8f4e21f4383715e9a0\n# branch.head feature/RW-0223价格政策禁用后需要获取到禁用状态\n# branch.upstream 洁柔/feature/RW-0223价�\n# branch.ab +0 -0\n```\nIs the remote branch name expected to be in valid Unicode?\n\nPlease also check if this issue occurs with [starship v1.23.0](https://github.com/starship/starship/releases/tag/v1.23.0), which executes git with different arguments to obtain the same information if the gitoxide backend is used.",
